# Kwalify Creative North Star (required)

Before proposing or implementing any design, UI, scene, animation, or visual change, read and comply with:

`docs/KWALIFY_CREATIVE_NORTH_STAR.md`

Illustration mode (visuals): `docs/KWALIFY_OBJECT_CONSTRUCTION_MODE.md` (Pets-style soft objects)  
Scene assembly: `docs/KWALIFY_EMOTIONAL_SCENE_ASSEMBLY.md`  
UI entry: `docs/EMOTION_GRID_UI_ENTRY.md` · Blueprint: `docs/KWALIFY_FINAL_UI_BLUEPRINT.md`  
Style DNA: `docs/KWALIFY_VISUAL_STYLE_DNA.md` · Heroes: `docs/KWALIFY_HERO_OBJECTS_LOCKED.md`

North Star overrides other docs when they conflict. See `docs/DOCUMENT_HIERARCHY.md`.

Core checks:
- Playlist is the primary product; mood visuals support feeling only
- Logged-in home: 5-card Pets-style grid → fullscreen illustrated object (no dashboard chrome)
- Spotify Pets **system** (clarity, one hero, soft illustration) — objects not animal mascots; no industrial/geometric icon UI
- Phase 1 art: soft `pump` illustration until language locked — [KWALIFY_PETROL_PUMP_SVG_LOCKED.md](docs/KWALIFY_PETROL_PUMP_SVG_LOCKED.md)
- Motion: gentle fade/scale only — no bounce, camera systems, or staged loaders
- If a feature does not improve 5-second clarity or 30-second "it gets me", do not prioritise it
